snippet.title: TheSDRShow
snippet.description:
The SDR Show (The Sex, Drugs, & Rock-n-Roll Show) is hosted by comedian Big Jay Oakerson and legendary radio host Ralph Sutton. 

SDR is a no-apologies, not politically correct, not for the faint of heart show that somehow blends the classic energy of a morning radio show into the new era of digital entertainment, and manages to separate itself from the literally 100s of 1000s of other shows out there. Every week Big Jay and Ralph interview comedians, celebrities, rock stars, adult film stars, and other legends. 

Tune in every Wednesday and Saturday for LIVE new episodes on https://www.GasDigitalNetwork.com or https://thesdrshow.com

Subscribe to our channel for the latest updates and don’t forget to hit the “bell” to receive notifications and to comment on our videos! 

Our show is a labor of love and we hope you enjoy listening to it as much as we enjoy doing it. Thank you!
